    "content": "<p>TrueLab Games, the independent studio behind Crazy Mix, may not be a household name like some of the bigger players in the industry, but don't let that fool you. These guys know how to make a killer slot game. In fact, we'd argue that Crazy Mix is proof that sometimes a smaller team can produce a game that's just as good as (if not better than) one made by a giant corporation.</p><p>Maybe it's because this underdog of a game studio has the freedom to get really creative without worrying about appeasing shareholders. Whatever the reason, we're just happy they made a game as fun as Crazy Mix.</p><p>With beautifully executed graphics and a unique theme that's both quirky and charming, it's hard not to love this game. And the bonuses and features are just plain wacky (in a good way). There's nothing quite like watching a trio of eggplants bouncing around on the reels.</p><p>So if you're tired of playing the same old slots from the same old developers, give Crazy Mix a shot. TrueLab Games may be new to the scene, but they're definitely ones to watch.</p>"
